!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
  %body
    %p
      Here is a weekly overview of regionless locations!
    %h3
      Regionless Weekly Overview
    %p
      %strong List of Empty Locations:
      %br
      - @machineless_locations.each do |ml|
        = ml
        %br
    %p
      %strong List of Suggested Locations:
      %br
      - @suggested_locations.each do |sl|
        = sl
        %br
    %p
      #{@suggested_locations_count} location(s) submitted
      %br
      #{@locations_added_count} location(s) added by you
      %br
      #{@locations_deleted_count} location(s) deleted
      %br
      #{@machine_comments_count} machine comment(s)
      %br
      #{@machines_added_count} machine(s) added
      %br
      #{@machines_removed_count} machine(s) removed
    %p
      Regionless is listing #{@machines_count} machines and #{@locations_count} locations
